<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">    &lt;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">description</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">&gt;Comprehensive PDF manipulation toolkit...&lt;/</span><span style="--shiki-light:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#85E89D;">description</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">&gt;</span></span>
